				Adobe_AGM_Utils/AGMUTIL_ndx 0/ddf cvx
				names_index Names length currentdict/srcStr get length 1 sub{
					1/index cvx/exch cvx/get cvx
					currentdict/dstStr get/AGMUTIL_ndx/load cvx 3 -1/roll cvx/put cvx
